### User Login (Get Token)
# @name login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "admin",
    "password": "password123"
}

###

@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Create Camera
POST http://localhost:5000/api/cameras
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Main Entrance",
    "streamURL": "rtsp://192.168.1.100:554/stream1",
    "location": "Entrance Hall",
    "status": "Active"
}

### Get All Cameras
GET http://localhost:5000/api/cameras
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Camera (Replace ID with actual ID from Create response)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/cameras/REPLACE_WITH_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Main Entrance Updated",
    "status": "Inactive"
}

### Delete Camera (Replace ID with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/cameras/REPLACE_WITH_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
